@startuml DangerMonitor_SP_GetFilter_Detailed
!theme plain
title CTS_MatchMonitor_Details_GetFilter - Detailed Database Flow

skinparam component {
    BackgroundColor lightblue
    BorderColor darkblue
}

skinparam database {
    BackgroundColor lightyellow
    BorderColor orange
}

skinparam arrow {
    Color darkgreen
}

package "SQL Server Database: bodb02 / WASAVerse" {
    database "bettrans" as BetTrans
    database "bettrans14" as BetTrans14
    database "bettrans_bk" as BetTransBK
    database "Match" as Match
    database "match14" as Match14
    database "match_bk" as MatchBK
    database "Customer" as Customer
    database "custInfo" as CustInfo
    database "Exchange" as Exchange
    database "Dep_CustSuper" as DepCustSuper
    database "CustProductStatus" as CustProductStatus
}

component "CTS_MatchMonitor_Details_GetFilter" as SP {
    note right
        **Database:** bodb02/WASAVerse
        **Purpose:** Get Filter Options for Detail Page
        **ViewMode:**
        - 0: All-MatchMonitor
        - 1: Suspicious Only
        - 2: All-Danger Monitor
    end note
}

' Temp Tables
package "Temp Tables (Internal)" {
    component "#tmpTrans" as TmpTrans
    component "#tmpSportBettype" as TmpSportBettype
    component "#tmpSuspiciousTrans" as TmpSuspiciousTrans
    component "#tmpSuspiciousDistinctTrans" as TmpSuspiciousDistinct
    component "#tmpUsername" as TmpUsername
    component "#tmpCustomer" as TmpCustomer
    component "@tmpBUMBData" as TmpBUMBData
}

note right of TmpTrans
    **Temp Table: #tmpTrans**
    * TransId : BIGINT
    * CustId : INT
    * Hdp1, Hdp2 : SMALLMONEY
    * LiveHomeScore, LiveAwayScore : SMALLINT
    * BetTeam : NVARCHAR(10)
    * CurrencyId : SMALLINT
    * CurrencyName : NVARCHAR(100)
    * Hdp : SMALLMONEY
    * IsLicensee : BIT
    * BetType : SMALLINT
    * TicketStatus : SMALLINT
    * Danger1-5 : TINYINT
    * CustomerClass : SMALLINT
    * SequenceId : BIGINT
    * TransDate : DATETIME
    * IsCashout : BIT
end note

note right of TmpSportBettype
    **Temp Table: #tmpSportBettype**
    * SportTypeID : SMALLINT
    * BetTypeID : INT
    * BetChoiceType : TINYINT
    * BetIDPattern : NVARCHAR(20)
    * BetID : BIGINT
end note

' Flow: Parse Input Parameters
SP --> TmpBUMBData : **EXEC**\nAge_SelBalanceUpDay
SP --> TmpBUMBData : **SELECT**\nGet BalanceUpDay, MoveBetsDay

SP --> TmpUsername : **INSERT**\n(Parse @UserNameList)
SP --> TmpCustomer : **INSERT**\n(Filter Customers by Username)

SP --> TmpSportBettype : **INSERT**\n(Parse @ListSportBettype JSON)

SP --> TmpSuspiciousTrans : **INSERT**\n(Parse @ListSuspiciousTransId JSON)
SP --> TmpSuspiciousDistinct : **INSERT**\n(DISTINCT TransIds)

' Flow: Determine Data Source
SP --> SP : Check EventDate vs\nBalanceUpDay/MoveBetsDay
note right of SP
    **Data Source Logic:**
    - EventDate < BalanceUpDay → Use bettrans_bk
    - EventDate <= MoveBetsDay → Use bettrans14
    - Otherwise → Use bettrans (Origin)
end note

' Flow: ViewMode = 1 (Suspicious Only)
SP --> TmpTrans : **INSERT**\n(ViewMode = 1)
TmpSuspiciousDistinct --> BetTrans : **JOIN**\nON TransId
BetTrans --> Match : **JOIN**\nON MatchId
BetTrans --> Exchange : **JOIN**\nON Currency
TmpSportBettype --> BetTrans : **JOIN**\nON SportType, BetType, BetID

note right of BetTrans
    **SELECT Operations (ViewMode=1):**
    - Filter by @MatchID
    - Filter by @IsLive
    - Filter by @IsExclTestCurr
    - Filter by @FromTransDate, @ToTransDate
    - Filter by @UserNameList
    - FROM bettrans (Origin)
    - FROM bettrans14 (14 days)
    - FROM bettrans_bk (Archive)
    - WITH(NOLOCK)
end note

' Flow: ViewMode = 0 (All-MatchMonitor)
SP --> TmpTrans : **INSERT**\n(ViewMode = 0)
BetTrans --> Match : **JOIN**\nON MatchId
BetTrans --> Exchange : **JOIN**\nON Currency
TmpSportBettype --> BetTrans : **JOIN**\nON SportType, BetType, BetID

' Flow: ViewMode = 2 (All-Danger Monitor)
SP --> TmpTrans : **INSERT**\n(ViewMode = 2)
BetTrans --> Match : **JOIN**\nON MatchId
BetTrans --> Customer : **JOIN**\nON CustId
BetTrans --> Exchange : **JOIN**\nON Currency
TmpSportBettype --> BetTrans : **JOIN**\nON SportType, BetType, BetID

note right of Customer
    **Filter Conditions (ViewMode=2):**
    - Exclude sites: Nextbet, 9wickets, 9wsports
    - Exclude username LIKE '%Cashout%'
    - Exclude specific mrecommend IDs
    - Exclude specific recommend IDs
    - Exclude specific srecommend IDs
end note

' Flow: Enrich Data with Customer Info
TmpTrans --> CustInfo : **JOIN**\nON CustId
CustInfo --> DepCustSuper : **JOIN**\nON srecommend
CustInfo --> CustProductStatus : **JOIN**\nON CustId

SP --> TmpTrans : **UPDATE**\n(Enrich with Customer Data)
note right of SP
    **UPDATE Operations:**
    - Set IsLicensee (from Dep_CustSuper)
    - Set Danger1-5 (from custInfo)
    - Set CustomerClass (from custInfo)
end note

' Flow: Return Filter Options
SP --> TmpTrans : **SELECT DISTINCT**
note right of SP
    **Returns:**
    - LiveHomeScore, LiveAwayScore
    - IsLicensee
    - CustomerClass
    - Danger1, Danger2, Danger3, Danger4, Danger5
    - CurrencyId, CurrencyName
    - SuspiciousReason, SuspiciousGroupId
    - Hdp, BetTeam
    - TicketStatus
    - IsCashout
    **Output Parameters:**
    - @MaxSequenceId
    - @MaxTransDate
    - @TotalTicketAll
    - @TotalTicketLicensee
    - @TotalTicketCredit
end note

' Cleanup
SP --> TmpTrans : **DROP TABLE**
SP --> TmpSportBettype : **DROP TABLE**
SP --> TmpSuspiciousTrans : **DROP TABLE**

@enduml

